Package: NNETARCH
Title: Neural Network Autoregressive Conditional Heteroskedasticity for Time Series Forecasting
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Rafael", "Montano", email = "rafael.montano@sydney.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a hybrid forecasting model combining nonlinear autoregression via neural networks (NNETAR) with volatility modeling using either GARCH or neural network-based residual modeling. This package extends the 'forecast' package functionality to provide variance-adaptive forecasting models for financial and economic time series.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
